WIP: integrate PCS provider in the merge.

Add new providers to the pacemaker module.  They provide the pcs part of
the pacemaker_* providers.  Currently only supporting:
 - pacemaker_order;
 - pacemaker_colocation;
 - pacmeaker_resource;

Those are the one use by the main Tripleo consumer of the project and
should provider a superset of the old module functionality.

